{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacePaddingInlineDefault"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token spaces.paddingInlineMedium"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"spacePaddingInlineDefault","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeTagComponentTokensProviderC25spacePaddingInlineDefaultSdvp","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spacePaddingInlineDefault"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetagcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddinginlinedefault"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider\/spacePaddingInlineDefault"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"]]},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of tag"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TagComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") ,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") , sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetagcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider/spacePaddingInlineDefault":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetagcomponenttokensprovider\/spacepaddinginlinedefault","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spacePaddingInlineDefault","kind":"identifier"},{"text